<h3>Contributors</h3>
<p>These are the people who are responsible for achieving the outcomes we intend. Contributors can create and edit all items in a project, including modifying the projects details and itâ€™s members. Contributors receive reminders and are notified when check-ins and debriefs are completed or overdue.</p>

<hr/>

<%- @contributors.each do |membership| %>
  <%#TODO:= current_user.email == membership.user_email ? '[Your membership]' : '' %>
