<h3>Stakeholders</h3>
<p>These are the people who needs to be consulted with or informed about the outcomes we intend. Stakeholders can view all items in a project and some of its details, but cannot modify its members or see check-ins. Stakeholders are notified when debriefs are completed.</p>

<hr/>

<%- @stakeholders.each do |membership| %>
